sub_title: Outdoor Life Coaching | Nature Quests to Ecuador, Ireland and Norway.
summary:
➙ Coaching & Nature in the Netherlands and Ecuador. 

➙ FOR WHOM? 

You want to follow your heart, but it is not that easy. 
You want to be in touch with your feelings, but how?
You need more confidence so you can make other choices.
You are looking for a deeper connection with yourself, others and nature. 

➙ WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU? 

As Outdoor Life Coach I work with and if possible in nature. If you are in the Netherlands I offer individual coaching programs in Drenthe. Adventurous women based in different parts of the world can join me on the next Coaching & Nature Trip to Ecuador in June 2020 and November 2020 or I can help you with coaching sessions by Skype or Face Time.  

➙ HOW DOES THIS HELP YOU?

You will get deeper insights in you obstacles and convictions. 
You will make choices in a different way, much closer to who you really are. 
You will be comfortable with yourself, also alone and in silence.
You will find out that vulnerability is also strength.
You will be able to give and receive. 
You dare to stop. Stand still and wait to see what shows on your path.
You will find new inspiration, and can follow your flow and intuition. 
You will feel free. 

➙CURIOUS?
Mail: info@katriendejong.nl
Web: www.katriendejong.nl
